'''Dragon's Spine''' was a large chain of snow-capped mountains on the [[Endor/Legends|forest moon]] of [[Endor (planet)/Legends|Endor]] at the edge of the [[Dragon's Pelt]]. [[Condor dragon/Legends|Condor dragons]] lived in caves inside the high peaks.

In [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]], [[Noa Briqualon]], [[Cindel Towani]], [[Wicket Wystri Warrick/Legends|Wicket Wystri Warrick]], and a group of [[Ewok/Legends|Ewoks]] from [[Bright Tree Village/Legends|Bright Tree Village]] escaped from [[Terak's Keep|Terak's castle]] in these mountains.

